  <trk>
    <name>Tour du Val d’Hérens: Cabane Becs de Bosson - Nax (Stage 5)</name>
    <desc>Scenic route from the high alpine mountain hut into the original and wild Vallon de Réchy and to Nax, which is also called &quot;Balcony of the Sky&quot; because of its location.</desc>
